Jamiʼin asusun tallafawa yara na MDD UNICEF kan cutar Ebola Peter Salama ya bayyana a ranar 3 ga wata cewa, a sakamakon yadda cutar ta yi mummanan tasiri ga kananan yara a kasashen yammacin Afirka masu fama da cutar Ebola, asusun zai kara yawan maʼaikatansa a kasashen daga 300 zuwa 600 don taimaka musu wajen yaki da cutar Ebola.

Salama ya bayyana a gun taron manema labaru da aka gudanar a cibiyar MDD dake birnin New York a wannan rana cewa, asusun zai kuma taimaka wajen tsugunar da yara marayu kimanin 4000 da suka rasa iyayensu sakamakon cutar ta Ebola.
(Zainab)

